"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-28-twisties-simone-biles-suffered-olympics-21311809\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"One of the greatest athletes in the history of theOlympics, Simone Biles, is due to make her bow in theParisGames.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 60, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American superstar already has four gold medals under her belt, but endured a torrid time of it Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 116, \"to\": 238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999124634481005, \"rank\": 7.54811375745946e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9963964480480383, \"rank\": 0.0036165590529644693, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Suffering from 'the twisties' Biles was forced to withdraw from several events and ultimately ended up taking a two-year hiatus from the sport she once dominated.\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest news on the Paris Olympics  Biles is far from alone in having faced a phenomena that is best described as a mental block that impact the spatial awareness of gymnasts.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old was particularly badly affected by the twisties during the vault competition during which her timing was well off as she struggled to nail her routine.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked to explain the twisties, Biles' teammate Laurie Hernandez explained: 'The rhythm is off, and your brain will like stutter step for half a second and that's enough to throw off the whole skill.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laurie Hernandez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laurie_Hernandez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And, so, it happens, and it takes a second to get over that.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Former U.S. national team member Aleah Finnegan gave her insight on Twitter, writing 'I have had the twisties since I was 11.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.999479361486017, \"rank\": 0.0002976924503861217, \"text\": \"U.S. national team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aleah Finnegan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aleah_Finnegan\"}, {\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.689884968758143e-14, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I cannot imagine the fear of having it happen to you during competition.'\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made a triumphant return to gymnastics and with her mental health now in a far better place, Biles is expecting to add to her Olympic legacy in Paris.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1397, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996730367, \"rank\": 3.26896071562561e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking last year, she said: 'I always kind of knew (I'd be back) as soon as everything that happened in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1511, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9963964480480383, \"rank\": 0.0036165590529644693, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, this time I am doing it for me.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked a lot on myself and I believe in myself a little bit more, just coming back out here and starting the first steps again.\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It means the world because after everything that kind of transpired in Tokyo and it took a lot.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9963964480480383, \"rank\": 0.0036165590529644693, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I worked on myself a lot, I still do therapy weekly and it's just been so exciting to come out here and have the confidence I had before.'\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"28 July - Team Qualifying: Simone Biles is making her first appearance in the team qualifying events.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will feature alongside her USA teammates (Jordan Chiles, Hezly Rivera and Sunisa Lee) in Subdivision 2 from 10:40am BST (11:40am CET and 5:40am ET).\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 2095, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"score\": 0.9999979751603442, \"rank\": 2.015519751691655e-06, \"text\": \"Rivera\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariano_Rivera\"}, {\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.9999999980645953, \"rank\": 1.935393834613597e-09, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"30 July - 